  <subfield code="a">Monte Carlo Threshold Energy Estimation for A + B → C + D processes: An Educational Resource in Experimental High Energy Physics Research</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">Sociedade Brasileira de Física</subfield>
 </datafield>
